		<title>林懿稅務講堂-第9集：收入調整項之傳統IRA</title>
		<link>./images/7052.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[jeel]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 27 Feb 2022 17:44:33 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[林懿稅務講堂]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[薪資稅]]></category>
